341
00:19:40.721 --> 00:19:41.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（京子）ああ
（美玲）でも…

342
00:19:42.347 --> 00:19:44.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
