372
00:21:20.028 --> 00:21:21.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何 言ってんだよ

373
00:21:22.572 --> 00:21:23.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
早く ざんげして！

374
00:21:27.035 --> 00:21:30.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
美穂のお父さん
早く この２人を落としてください

375
00:21:31.164 --> 00:21:33.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
そして 私たちを解放してください

376
00:21:34.960 --> 00:21:35.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
美玲

377
00:21:36.670 --> 00:21:38.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
お前 狂ったのか？

378
00:21:41.258 --> 00:21:42.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（彩花）もう 分かったよ！

379
00:21:44.803 --> 00:21:46.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
この写真は…

380
00:21:46.555 --> 00:21:47.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
私だよ

381
00:21:47.973 --> 00:21:48.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（芽実）そうなの？

382
00:21:50.267 --> 00:21:51.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
私の軽はずみな行動が

383
00:21:52.561 --> 00:21:55.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
美穂のお父さんに
迷惑かけたのは謝る

384
00:21:55.939 --> 00:21:57.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
でも わざとなんかじゃ…

385
00:21:59.234 --> 00:22:01.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ホントに美穂のお父さんなんて
知らなかった！

386
00:22:02.362 --> 00:22:04.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（久美）美玲 信じてあげようよ

387
00:22:04.698 --> 00:22:05.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（芽実）そうだよ

388
00:22:08.827 --> 00:22:10.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（彩花）イヤー！
（水音）

389
00:22:12.414 --> 00:22:13.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
水が…

390
00:22:14.499 --> 00:22:15.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
水が！

391
00:22:18.754 --> 00:22:19.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
彩花！

392
00:22:20.505 --> 00:22:21.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（彩花）私…

393
00:22:22.716 --> 00:22:23.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
