394
00:22:24.968 --> 00:22:25.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
大丈夫！

395
00:22:26.094 --> 00:22:28.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
