396
00:22:29.431 --> 00:22:30.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ごめんね

397
00:22:32.559 --> 00:22:33.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
私…

398
00:22:34.603 --> 00:22:36.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
“真っ白な正義”なんて
