402
00:22:48.784 --> 00:22:49.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
“卒業したら…”

403
00:22:50.786 --> 00:22:52.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
